== A . 讀取 Python 版本 (Windows 10)
CMD: python --version
Output: Python 3.11.3

== B. 清除 shell
>>> print("\n" * 100)

== C. 清除 shell
import os
os.system('cls||clear')

== D. 清除 shell
import subprocess, platform

if platform.system()=="Windows":
    if platform.release() in {"10", "11"}:
        subprocess.run("", shell=True) #Needed to fix a bug regarding Windows 10; not sure about Windows 11
        print("\033c", end="")
    else:
        subprocess.run(["cls"])
else: #Linux and Mac
    print("\033c", end="")

(按 Enter 兩次)
